Execute step {{current_step}} of {{total_steps}}.

Same rigor as step 1 — no tail degradation, you have no fatigue. This step must serve the deliverable: {{understand-task.expected_deliverable}}. If the remaining plan no longer fits what's been built — teleport-replan.

